title: All The Cold - Manvantara (2015)
description:
After almost a year's delay, our first full-length album finally came out. "Manvantara" is a kind of continuation of the previous EP "Heritage" (2013) in sound and ideas, we have expanded and deepened them, so expect the most daring and experimental stuff for all time.

Track list:
1. Time Prophet
2. Viaje a Ixtlan
3. Insectlord
4. Tramp Side, Vendella For Taja
5. Absorption Of The Planet
6. The Unmanifested
7. Underlove Elements
8. (We Will Honour The Past, And...) Fight To The Last
